WEBVTT

01:37.770 --> 01:40.620
[Fate Chooses You]

01:41.240 --> 01:43.690
[Episode 5]

01:54.120 --> 01:55.870
Primordial spirit stabilize the soul.

01:55.870 --> 01:58.000
A thousand lanterns, guided by blood.

01:58.070 --> 01:58.509
Rise!

02:13.030 --> 02:14.080
Immortal spells?

02:14.750 --> 02:15.880
What are they doing?

02:16.520 --> 02:17.250
I don't know.

02:18.079 --> 02:19.079
But for Xin Mei,

02:19.520 --> 02:20.850
this is not a good thing.

03:15.470 --> 03:16.130
Chengying.

03:17.190 --> 03:17.560
Go.

03:55.240 --> 03:56.570
It's the War Demon! Run!

04:00.680 --> 04:01.880
Don't eat me! Please!

05:15.750 --> 05:16.330
This way.

05:29.310 --> 05:30.310
You're cornered.

05:30.680 --> 05:31.920
If you are willing to repent,

05:31.920 --> 05:33.720
and there may be a way out for you.

05:33.830 --> 05:34.360
Go, now.

05:42.000 --> 05:42.600
This is...

05:43.680 --> 05:45.880
Are you a disciple of the Tianyuan Sect?

05:46.190 --> 05:46.750
No.

05:47.159 --> 05:49.220
Then do you know Senior Bai Zongying?

05:49.880 --> 05:51.140
Are we fighting or not?

05:51.270 --> 05:52.400
If not, I'm leaving.

05:52.680 --> 05:53.880
You're asking for it.

06:36.830 --> 06:37.430
Come here.

06:38.000 --> 06:38.530
Hurry up!

06:40.750 --> 06:42.040
Here. Hide inside.

06:43.870 --> 06:44.800
-Mei.
-Mei.

06:45.560 --> 06:46.720
I can't protect all of you.

06:46.720 --> 06:47.780
Don't make a sound.

06:48.000 --> 06:49.390
Stay hidden.

06:51.600 --> 06:52.480
Mei.

06:56.100 --> 06:57.450
You are in such a hurry—

06:59.310 --> 07:00.750
where are you going?

07:01.390 --> 07:02.120
Go find her.

07:02.830 --> 07:03.600
Have fun.

07:43.600 --> 07:44.950
A mere Qi Refining cultivator

07:44.950 --> 07:46.680
really worth all this trouble?

07:46.800 --> 07:48.360
I suggest you surrender.

07:48.560 --> 07:49.620
My time is limited.

07:50.310 --> 07:52.040
My master is expecting me back.

07:56.870 --> 07:58.950
You always talk about your master.

07:59.800 --> 08:00.750
Nangong Guhong.

08:01.120 --> 08:02.450
How old are you exactly?

08:02.600 --> 08:04.200
Haven't you been weaned yet?

08:04.430 --> 08:06.190
Or has your moral sense gone astray,

08:06.190 --> 08:07.000
that you've developed

08:07.000 --> 08:09.160
such a despicable feeling for your master?

08:09.160 --> 08:10.820
Are you planning to marry her?

08:16.680 --> 08:18.480
Don't be afraid, Immortal Lady.

08:18.950 --> 08:21.080
I don't want to make things difficult.

08:21.310 --> 08:23.310
But you killed one of my sect members

08:23.560 --> 08:25.690
and destroyed this magical artifact.

08:25.720 --> 08:27.560
I have no choice but
to take you back with me

08:27.560 --> 08:29.420
to give my people an explanation.

08:30.160 --> 08:31.270
You and that Mr. Gui

08:31.870 --> 08:33.130
are from the same sect?

08:33.669 --> 08:34.270
Yes.

08:34.840 --> 08:36.440
But I'm not here for revenge.

08:37.320 --> 08:39.240
I'm simply just following the orders

08:39.240 --> 08:40.440
to fight against you.

08:40.960 --> 08:43.440
Why don't you come with me quietly?

08:44.000 --> 08:46.390
I promise to leave your body intact.

08:47.910 --> 08:49.080
Birds of a feather.

08:49.870 --> 08:51.870
Since you refuse to listen to reason,

08:51.870 --> 08:53.670
then I'll have to use force.

08:57.670 --> 08:58.790
Sir you certainly

08:58.790 --> 09:00.120
have made quite a scene—

09:00.670 --> 09:02.000
breaking my formation,

09:02.200 --> 09:04.060
humiliating the immortal sects,

09:04.630 --> 09:06.890
and now you're trying to save that woman?

09:06.960 --> 09:08.480
It seems like you're deliberately

09:08.480 --> 09:10.280
making things difficult for me.

09:17.080 --> 09:18.840
This is the Dragon Prison Formation,

09:18.840 --> 09:20.910
a masterpiece I've devoted my life to.

09:20.910 --> 09:22.030
The twenty-four Gates of Life

09:22.030 --> 09:23.030
have been sealed,

09:23.200 --> 09:25.270
and the thirty-six Paths of Death
have been blocked as well.

09:25.270 --> 09:26.840
As they say,
"There's neither road to heaven

09:26.840 --> 09:28.240
nor door into the earth."

09:28.360 --> 09:29.910
Even a Golden Core cultivator

09:29.910 --> 09:31.240
would struggle to break it.

09:31.240 --> 09:31.960
Now then,

09:32.150 --> 09:34.080
can we have a proper conversation?

09:34.120 --> 09:35.450
Has anyone ever told you

09:35.790 --> 09:37.150
you talk too much?

09:46.120 --> 09:46.720
You...

09:47.240 --> 09:49.500
What exactly is your cultivation level?

09:49.840 --> 09:50.840
I've never bothered to count.

09:50.840 --> 09:52.200
But it's more than enough

09:52.200 --> 09:53.600
to break your formation.

10:10.910 --> 10:11.710
Flute player,

10:12.150 --> 10:13.550
what are you waiting for?

10:19.750 --> 10:20.360
Useless.

10:20.610 --> 10:22.010
You can't even land a hit.

10:22.320 --> 10:23.050
Without you,

10:23.670 --> 10:25.470
I'd have taken her down long ago.

11:04.080 --> 11:06.320
The Chengying Sword
does not strike the nameless.

11:06.320 --> 11:07.360
Tell me your name.

11:07.600 --> 11:08.840
You talk too much.

11:38.550 --> 11:40.080
You betrayed your Dao heart

11:40.230 --> 11:42.070
by interfering in mortal affairs.

11:42.070 --> 11:43.790
That alone condemns you to death.

11:43.790 --> 11:45.050
Dragging us into this—

11:45.320 --> 11:47.120
that sin is beyond forgiveness.

11:57.030 --> 11:58.490
Still won't admit defeat?

11:58.510 --> 11:59.770
As long as I'm not dead,

12:00.000 --> 12:01.000
I have not lost.

12:45.050 --> 12:49.800
♪ Being haunted by the spell,
even if it's cruel ♪

12:49.950 --> 12:53.060
♪ It's better than being trapped by fate ♪

12:53.080 --> 12:54.720
♪ Between gain and loss ♪

12:54.850 --> 12:58.800
♪ Lies a thousand years of grace ♪

12:54.910 --> 12:55.870
The book says,

12:56.440 --> 12:58.510
once you replaced the body,
you'll be able to see color.

12:58.510 --> 12:59.910
It should be soon, right?

13:01.010 --> 13:04.180
♪ Soul consumed, bones remade—
I accept it all ♪

13:04.290 --> 13:08.020
♪ Embracing pain as home,
reborn like a phoenix ♪

13:08.360 --> 13:14.450
♪ Just to trade the rest of my days
for one true life as a human ♪

13:15.380 --> 13:19.040
♪ Let strong wine carry me into
drunken nights till midnight ♪

13:19.070 --> 13:22.130
♪ Let my soul blaze in brilliant colors ♪

13:22.150 --> 13:24.980
♪ Let the agony of a thousand cuts ♪

13:25.010 --> 13:29.600
♪ Stand as proof that I have lived ♪

13:29.890 --> 13:33.490
♪ Let me taste a life of flesh and blood
in full ♪

13:33.520 --> 13:36.670
♪ Let me savor the many flavors
of the mortal world ♪

13:36.880 --> 13:38.700
♪ Let me face the world's
warmth and cold alike ♪

13:38.720 --> 13:44.060
♪ To live and perish with it,
daring to go mad, daring to dream ♪

13:44.090 --> 13:50.020
♪ Don't live in vain,
have a pleasant journey of life ♪

13:58.340 --> 14:03.080
♪ Being haunted by the spell,
even if it's cruel ♪

14:03.240 --> 14:06.350
♪ It's better than being trapped by fate ♪

14:06.370 --> 14:08.010
♪ Between gain and loss ♪

14:08.130 --> 14:12.090
♪ Lies a thousand years of grace ♪

14:13.870 --> 14:14.870
Give a dog a bad name

14:14.300 --> 14:17.470
♪ Soul consumed, bones remade—
I accept it all ♪

14:15.080 --> 14:16.030
and hang him.

14:16.750 --> 14:18.000
Though we haven't interacted much,

14:17.580 --> 14:21.310
♪ Embracing pain as home,
reborn like a phoenix ♪

14:18.480 --> 14:20.120
I feel that you're not the same as

14:20.120 --> 14:21.650
what's being said about you out there.

14:21.650 --> 14:27.740
♪ Just to trade the rest of my days
for one true life as a human ♪

14:22.030 --> 14:22.870
If you were truly

14:22.870 --> 14:24.070
greedy and cowardly,

14:24.360 --> 14:26.440
you'd have come asking me for help, right?

14:26.440 --> 14:27.960
After all, in the eyes of the world,

14:27.960 --> 14:29.000
I'm also a cultivator.

14:28.090 --> 14:31.690
♪ Let me taste a life of flesh and blood
in full ♪

14:30.750 --> 14:31.270
You...

14:31.710 --> 14:34.870
♪ Let me savor the many flavors
of the mortal world ♪

14:32.080 --> 14:33.810
you don't want to live anymore?

14:35.070 --> 14:36.890
♪ Let me face the world's
warmth and cold alike ♪

14:36.920 --> 14:42.260
♪ To live and perish with it,
daring to go mad, daring to dream ♪

14:42.280 --> 14:48.220
♪ Don't live in vain,
have a pleasant journey of life ♪

14:50.600 --> 14:51.320
Is it heavy?

14:51.870 --> 14:52.440
No.

14:58.870 --> 14:59.400
Quickly.

15:13.000 --> 15:14.030
What is this?

15:18.360 --> 15:19.690
It looks like medicine.

15:20.630 --> 15:21.230
Medicine?

15:22.080 --> 15:23.720
Is it to treat Mei's wounds?

15:25.750 --> 15:26.750
Who gave it to her?

15:27.720 --> 15:28.550
I don't know.

15:29.200 --> 15:30.330
We can't just use it.

15:30.510 --> 15:32.110
We don't even know where it came from.

15:32.110 --> 15:33.240
What if it's poison?

15:52.440 --> 15:52.840
Lu.

15:53.320 --> 15:54.450
How is Immortal Xin?

15:55.670 --> 15:56.360
Find a way

15:56.550 --> 15:57.610
to make her take it.

15:59.670 --> 16:01.930
Isn't this your own life-saving elixir?

16:03.790 --> 16:05.030
Haven't you already given her

16:05.030 --> 16:06.960
the Hidden-heart Orchid
to restore her Qihai?

16:06.960 --> 16:08.160
Why give her this too?

16:08.550 --> 16:09.610
Just give it to her.

16:10.550 --> 16:12.320
First a magical artifact, then flowers,

16:12.320 --> 16:14.030
and now even your life-saving elixir.

16:14.030 --> 16:14.630
Lu,

16:15.630 --> 16:17.830
you're feeling bad for her, aren't you?

16:19.240 --> 16:19.640
Right.

16:20.120 --> 16:21.750
If it were me, I'd feel the same.

16:21.750 --> 16:23.080
What Immortal Xin did

16:23.200 --> 16:24.400
was truly righteous.

16:24.910 --> 16:26.640
She has only met you a few times,

16:27.320 --> 16:29.320
yet she risked her life for you

16:29.480 --> 16:31.210
and ended up severely injured.

16:31.480 --> 16:32.940
Tell me, what is she after?

16:33.790 --> 16:35.850
Could it be that she's fallen for you?

16:36.360 --> 16:37.960
If you end up like her one day,

16:38.240 --> 16:39.900
I would feel sorry for you too.

16:41.030 --> 16:41.910
That doesn't sound

16:41.910 --> 16:42.910
like a good thing.

16:44.080 --> 16:45.360
But I'm in a good mood today.

16:45.360 --> 16:46.670
Let me take you somewhere

16:46.670 --> 16:47.750
to broaden your horizons.

16:47.750 --> 16:48.910
Broaden my horizons?

16:48.910 --> 16:49.440
Let's go.

16:49.480 --> 16:51.140
You'll see when you get there.

16:52.010 --> 16:54.420
[Liang Residence]

17:05.030 --> 17:06.089
My senior has left?

17:06.680 --> 17:07.069
Yes.

17:08.030 --> 17:09.790
Young Sect Leader Lin left a letter,

17:09.790 --> 17:11.349
saying he had an epiphany at Lingtai,

17:11.349 --> 17:12.720
and feared an impending tribulation,

17:12.720 --> 17:14.640
so he returned to his sect
for secluded meditation.

17:14.640 --> 17:16.030
Senior Jin, you just arrived in the city.

17:16.030 --> 17:17.750
Have you discovered anything?

17:17.750 --> 17:18.609
I came too late.

17:19.000 --> 17:20.030
By the time I got here,

17:20.030 --> 17:21.560
the fight was already over.

17:27.109 --> 17:28.030
Immortals,

17:28.400 --> 17:29.510
did Immortal Lin

17:29.640 --> 17:31.590
flee the battle

17:31.790 --> 17:33.790
because he was frightened
by that enchantress?

17:33.790 --> 17:34.590
Do you really think that female cultivator

17:34.590 --> 17:35.990
is some powerful figure?

17:36.030 --> 17:37.720
She's just a cultivator
at the Qi Refining stage.

17:37.720 --> 17:38.880
What is there to fear?

17:38.880 --> 17:40.070
Qi Refining stage?

17:40.440 --> 17:41.830
And yet, with all of you surrounding her,

17:41.830 --> 17:43.830
she still managed to escape, right?

17:49.270 --> 17:50.750
I know

17:50.880 --> 17:53.010
that your abilities are exceptional.

17:53.110 --> 17:55.270
But the longer this drags on,
the more dangerous it becomes.

17:55.270 --> 17:57.000
That enchantress is still out there,

17:57.000 --> 17:58.530
which is quite unsettling.

17:58.830 --> 17:59.550
Why not

17:59.920 --> 18:02.270
write a letter to your sect elders

18:02.590 --> 18:03.850
and ask for their help?

18:04.000 --> 18:05.440
So we can put an end to this mess

18:05.440 --> 18:06.570
as soon as possible.

18:06.920 --> 18:09.110
Does she deserve
my master's intervention?

18:09.110 --> 18:11.160
Whether she does or not isn't the point.

18:11.160 --> 18:12.070
The real deal is—

18:12.070 --> 18:13.930
how do we catch that enchantress?

18:18.000 --> 18:19.240
Back then, the Imperial Court

18:19.240 --> 18:20.750
made a pact

18:21.310 --> 18:22.920
with the Twelve Immortal Sects.

18:22.920 --> 18:24.850
The Court permitted
them to exist,

18:25.360 --> 18:26.310
to take in disciples,
to preach their ways,

18:26.310 --> 18:27.400
and to establish their own sects.

18:27.400 --> 18:29.180
But the immortal sects
are also obligated to help the Court

18:29.180 --> 18:30.110
to maintain order—

18:30.110 --> 18:32.270
strictly forbidding any cultivator
from entering the mortal world

18:32.270 --> 18:34.530
to interfere with the empire's affairs.

18:37.200 --> 18:38.830
But later,
unaffiliated cultivators emerged,

18:38.830 --> 18:39.640
ignoring the rules.

18:39.640 --> 18:41.440
Then we have the evil sect,
which is also uncontrollable.

18:41.440 --> 18:43.070
They entered the path
without establishing a Dao heart,

18:43.070 --> 18:44.440
doing whatever they want.

18:44.440 --> 18:45.900
They are utterly lawless!

18:46.070 --> 18:47.750
Even so, it would have been manageable—

18:47.750 --> 18:49.160
as long as the Twelve Immortal Sects

18:49.160 --> 18:50.400
kept them in check.

18:50.590 --> 18:51.590
But look at the state of things now!

18:51.590 --> 18:53.000
Even a mere Qi Refining cultivator

18:53.000 --> 18:54.830
can walk through the capital
as if she owns it.

18:54.830 --> 18:55.920
What kind of rule is this?

18:55.920 --> 18:57.580
And what kind of world is this?

18:58.210 --> 18:59.320
I am speaking!

18:59.350 --> 19:00.830
Can you play that flute later?

19:00.830 --> 19:02.030
What's your problem?

19:08.830 --> 19:10.290
My Lord, please sit tight.

19:13.640 --> 19:14.240
Well...

19:15.000 --> 19:16.110
Immortal Masters,

19:16.640 --> 19:18.830
do you have any other solutions?

19:19.200 --> 19:19.640
Wait.

19:20.070 --> 19:21.030
Just wait?

19:21.270 --> 19:21.720
Yes.

19:22.550 --> 19:23.880
Wait for her to kill you.

19:27.400 --> 19:28.480
You are her target.

19:28.920 --> 19:30.050
Until she kills you,

19:30.400 --> 19:32.130
she will not leave the capital.

19:32.270 --> 19:32.830
So,

19:33.270 --> 19:34.400
as long as you are here,

19:34.400 --> 19:35.270
she will come.

19:37.200 --> 19:38.400
A weak woman like her—

19:38.960 --> 19:40.680
knowing so many people are after her—

19:40.680 --> 19:42.740
you think she'd still dare to show up?

19:47.030 --> 19:48.490
Still won't admit defeat?

19:48.510 --> 19:49.770
As long as I'm not dead,

19:50.070 --> 19:51.030
I have not lost.

19:56.400 --> 19:57.160
She will.

19:58.270 --> 19:59.270
Just wait and see.

20:05.590 --> 20:07.310
You don't need to put on a long face.

20:07.310 --> 20:08.200
With us here,

20:08.510 --> 20:09.720
that head of yours

20:09.880 --> 20:10.830
will stay safely

20:10.880 --> 20:11.940
right on your neck.

20:46.750 --> 20:47.280
Brother.

20:47.400 --> 20:48.070
Hurry up!

20:48.200 --> 20:48.750
Coming!

20:50.800 --> 20:52.240
Be careful—don't spill it.

20:52.240 --> 20:52.830
Okay.

20:59.440 --> 21:01.310
Immortal Lady.

21:01.830 --> 21:02.960
You're awake.

21:18.160 --> 21:19.160
Immortal Lady,

21:19.440 --> 21:21.200
please eat.

21:27.720 --> 21:29.110
My brother and I

21:29.310 --> 21:31.110
just picked these from the tree.

21:31.200 --> 21:32.260
They're not dirty.

21:39.000 --> 21:39.830
So,

21:40.400 --> 21:42.590
you are Lu Huai's children?

21:42.920 --> 21:43.940
We are his foster children.

21:43.940 --> 21:45.270
Lord Lu was kind to us.

21:45.480 --> 21:46.210
When he died,

21:46.310 --> 21:48.110
no one burned offerings for him,
or swept his tomb.

21:48.110 --> 21:49.510
So we kowtowed on our own,

21:49.650 --> 21:51.440
and saw him as our foster father.

21:51.440 --> 21:53.160
Father was very good to us.

21:53.680 --> 21:54.680
When he was alive,

21:54.920 --> 21:56.590
he often brought us food.

21:57.440 --> 21:59.750
Later, he was locked up.

22:00.240 --> 22:02.770
Then those people came
and smashed the house.

22:03.160 --> 22:04.760
My brother and I stayed there

22:05.160 --> 22:07.090
to watch over the house for Father.

22:07.510 --> 22:08.640
We thought

22:09.000 --> 22:12.270
he'd come back one day.

22:13.480 --> 22:14.400
But...

22:18.590 --> 22:20.310
So you saved me

22:20.830 --> 22:21.720
because of him?

22:22.240 --> 22:23.640
You gave Father a proper burial.

22:23.640 --> 22:24.840
You are a good person.

22:28.510 --> 22:30.310
Wei County is so far from the capital.

22:30.310 --> 22:31.750
Why did you two come all the way here?

22:31.750 --> 22:33.280
Because you can avenge him.

22:33.640 --> 22:34.530
Only you would,

22:34.680 --> 22:36.340
and only you could avenge him.

22:36.440 --> 22:37.310
You are an immortal.

22:37.310 --> 22:39.200
Immortals protect good people.

22:40.830 --> 22:41.960
I'm not an immortal.

22:42.200 --> 22:43.460
I'm just a cultivator.

22:44.000 --> 22:45.000
It's all the same.

22:46.920 --> 22:48.690
Last time, when I fought

22:48.720 --> 22:49.790
that black-robed elder,

22:49.790 --> 22:51.450
were you the ones who saved me?

22:51.830 --> 22:52.760
You were injured

22:52.960 --> 22:54.000
and passed out.

22:54.400 --> 22:56.330
So we dragged you back to the house.

22:57.000 --> 22:58.600
But this time was different.

22:58.750 --> 23:00.550
The soldiers were everywhere—

23:01.070 --> 23:02.880
arresting people across the city.

23:02.880 --> 23:03.940
It was terrifying.

23:04.200 --> 23:06.030
So we didn't dare stay anymore.

23:09.110 --> 23:10.110
Then this time...

23:10.510 --> 23:11.720
where did you find me?

23:12.070 --> 23:12.750
At the ruined house.

23:12.750 --> 23:13.400
That night,

23:13.400 --> 23:14.860
you hid us in the haystack.

23:15.030 --> 23:16.360
We didn't dare come out.

23:16.690 --> 23:19.030
We stayed until dawn,
then went back to the house.

23:19.030 --> 23:19.580
The moment we opened the door,

23:19.580 --> 23:21.440
we found you unconscious inside.

23:21.440 --> 23:22.070
Then we

23:22.070 --> 23:23.070
brought you here.

23:23.790 --> 23:24.790
The ruined house?

23:25.830 --> 23:26.960
But I remember

23:27.190 --> 23:29.060
I passed out on the street.

23:29.720 --> 23:31.250
Someone must have saved me.

23:31.880 --> 23:33.070
Did you see anyone?

23:33.680 --> 23:34.520
No.

23:34.720 --> 23:36.000
Me neither.

23:42.210 --> 23:43.340
You haven't eaten?

23:52.960 --> 23:53.960
We're not hungry.

23:53.960 --> 23:55.820
I'll take Jiujiu out to eat later.

24:01.240 --> 24:02.440
Here, have one first.

24:06.750 --> 24:08.210
Thank you, Immortal Lady.

24:09.200 --> 24:10.860
Didn't you call me Mei before?

24:10.960 --> 24:12.640
Just call me that.

24:14.200 --> 24:15.070
We heard

24:15.400 --> 24:16.960
you were our foster father's wife.

24:16.960 --> 24:18.690
But we followed him for so long,

24:18.720 --> 24:20.480
we never once saw him get married.

24:20.480 --> 24:21.160
Back in Wei County,

24:21.160 --> 24:22.270
many beautiful young women

24:22.270 --> 24:23.270
liked our foster father.

24:23.270 --> 24:25.400
They even sent matchmakers to propose,

24:25.400 --> 24:26.930
but he turned them all down.

24:26.960 --> 24:27.480
What exactly

24:27.480 --> 24:29.280
was your relationship with him?

24:29.350 --> 24:30.010
Were you two

24:30.160 --> 24:31.560
really husband and wife?

25:05.920 --> 25:06.440
Lu,

25:07.160 --> 25:08.160
don't just drink.

25:08.400 --> 25:09.000
Come here.

25:09.860 --> 25:11.830
So this is
the horizon-broadening experience

25:11.830 --> 25:14.750
you insisted on bringing me to see
instead of delivering my medicine?

25:14.750 --> 25:15.270
Yeah.

25:16.270 --> 25:17.200
I've reserved

25:17.310 --> 25:19.440
the entire Zuixian Restaurant today.

25:19.590 --> 25:21.350
Bridges like starlight, trees like fire.

25:21.350 --> 25:23.550
Ten thousand red lotuses in full bloom.

25:23.680 --> 25:25.280
The dancers are enchanting,

25:25.640 --> 25:27.240
the music lingers in the air.

25:27.750 --> 25:29.000
With fine wine to drink

25:29.000 --> 25:30.400
and paintings to admire—

25:30.400 --> 25:31.510
what more

25:32.070 --> 25:33.800
could one possibly ask of life?

25:34.750 --> 25:36.590
Only if you can actually get it.

25:37.030 --> 25:38.290
To me, a place like this

25:38.310 --> 25:39.110
is nothing

25:40.110 --> 25:41.070
but a headache

25:41.480 --> 25:42.340
and an eyesore.

25:48.440 --> 25:49.480
Everything in this world

25:49.480 --> 25:51.240
has to stay in balance.

25:52.440 --> 25:53.440
Just like Tai Chi—

25:54.020 --> 25:55.280
yin and yang opposing each other.

25:55.280 --> 25:57.350
One must give up something
to gain something else.

25:57.350 --> 25:58.160
You War Demons

25:58.160 --> 25:59.640
are born with powerful physiques,

25:59.640 --> 26:01.270
and lightning cultivation speed.

26:01.270 --> 26:03.200
Even your blood has healing power.

26:03.480 --> 26:04.550
If you were just like mortals

26:04.550 --> 26:05.680
in every other way,

26:05.880 --> 26:07.440
wouldn't you be having

26:07.720 --> 26:09.520
all the advantages in the world?

26:11.680 --> 26:13.240
That's a punishment from the gods.

26:13.240 --> 26:14.640
I know it's a punishment.

26:15.070 --> 26:17.070
I'm just trying
to give you a new way to look at it.

26:17.070 --> 26:18.200
Think of it this way.

26:18.270 --> 26:20.640
Mortals must endure
great trials and tribulations

26:20.640 --> 26:22.170
if they want to become gods.

26:22.920 --> 26:24.250
For you to become human,

26:24.400 --> 26:26.000
you must go through the same.

26:26.200 --> 26:26.880
Does that

26:27.310 --> 26:28.790
make you feel a bit better?

26:30.440 --> 26:31.040
Not at all.

26:44.310 --> 26:45.030
I know.

26:45.720 --> 26:48.070
War Demons are brutal and bloodthirsty.

26:48.480 --> 26:49.940
Your bodies are powerful,

26:50.240 --> 26:51.590
yet you feel no pain.

26:52.110 --> 26:53.270
You don't feel pain yourselves,

26:53.270 --> 26:55.530
and you don't care whether others bleed—

26:56.110 --> 26:57.240
then you become mad.

26:57.830 --> 27:00.350
Everything you taste is foul and rotten,

27:00.830 --> 27:01.880
but for survival,

27:02.200 --> 27:04.060
you must swallow it day after day.

27:04.110 --> 27:05.920
What others call delicacies,

27:06.350 --> 27:07.590
to War Demons,

27:07.880 --> 27:09.540
are nothing but filthy swill—

27:10.270 --> 27:11.670
then you become envious.

27:11.830 --> 27:13.630
You know the turn of day and night

27:13.920 --> 27:15.680
and the changing of seasons,

27:16.230 --> 27:18.490
yet you can never sleep,
not for a single night.

27:18.490 --> 27:19.770
A lifetime spent

27:20.070 --> 27:21.510
without ever knowing a dream—

27:21.510 --> 27:22.910
then you become anxious.

27:22.960 --> 27:25.590
They say the world is a tapestry
of a thousand colors,

27:25.590 --> 27:26.790
bright and dazzling,

27:27.270 --> 27:28.550
yet you can't see them,

27:28.750 --> 27:31.030
so it's just boring and lifeless.

27:31.550 --> 27:34.400
To you, a beauty is no different
from a shura-demon;

27:34.400 --> 27:35.480
a prosperous world

27:35.510 --> 27:37.510
is no different from the Avici Hell—

27:39.110 --> 27:40.840
then you become cold-blooded.

27:41.070 --> 27:42.270
A life like this

27:42.510 --> 27:44.000
may seem

27:44.830 --> 27:46.630
completely meaningless to you.

27:47.270 --> 27:48.000
But now,

27:48.590 --> 27:49.830
you've found a way.

27:50.400 --> 27:52.310
If you can endure these five trials:

27:52.310 --> 27:52.920
the replacing of the flesh,

27:52.920 --> 27:54.030
the bone, the blood, and the heart.

27:54.030 --> 27:55.160
As long as you pass these five trials,

27:55.160 --> 27:56.440
you will be reborn

27:56.920 --> 27:57.960
as a human!

27:58.830 --> 27:59.480
Lu,

28:00.680 --> 28:02.480
you can already sleep peacefully,

28:02.480 --> 28:04.540
And soon you will be able to see color.

28:04.590 --> 28:06.650
You are not like the other War Demons.

28:06.880 --> 28:08.110
Your Avici Hell

28:08.680 --> 28:10.420
already has a ray of light!

28:11.200 --> 28:11.590
Come.

28:12.350 --> 28:15.000
Today, let me teach you ahead of time,

28:15.480 --> 28:16.510
and see what colors

28:16.510 --> 28:18.270
truly look like in this world.

28:21.440 --> 28:24.720
Distant mountains wear a misty grey,
soft and stretching far.

28:24.720 --> 28:28.000
Cool strings of the lute
chase the sunset glow in a wine cup.

28:28.640 --> 28:29.110
Lu,

28:30.110 --> 28:32.400
this is the Mountain-Mist Grey.

28:33.880 --> 28:35.160
Thank you for the compliment, Sir.

28:35.160 --> 28:37.400
Mild husks of grain, tender as rice water;

28:37.400 --> 28:39.930
golden cups sway
as the wind ripens the paddy.

28:40.830 --> 28:41.310
This is

28:41.830 --> 28:43.160
the Rice-Cream Yellow.

28:43.350 --> 28:45.070
And this is the Golden Yellow.

28:47.960 --> 28:50.270
In April, green plums are small as beans,

28:50.480 --> 28:53.110
while loquats in the forest
are ripe and plump.

28:53.750 --> 28:55.440
But this isn't a loquat,

28:56.240 --> 28:57.880
nor is it a green plum.

29:03.920 --> 29:04.400
This...

29:05.070 --> 29:06.330
is the true Plum Green.

29:07.920 --> 29:08.960
I can't distinguish

29:08.960 --> 29:10.490
any of what you were saying.

29:11.830 --> 29:13.030
I just want to ask you,

29:13.750 --> 29:15.880
what color is your collar?

29:17.750 --> 29:18.510
Red.

29:20.550 --> 29:21.400
Red?

29:47.240 --> 29:47.880
Lu,

29:49.240 --> 29:50.310
you can see red?

29:51.010 --> 29:51.490
Yes.

29:52.330 --> 29:53.050
I can...

29:53.880 --> 29:54.880
see red now.

29:57.400 --> 29:57.920
Lu,

29:58.110 --> 29:59.590
you can see red!

29:59.720 --> 30:01.270
You can see color now!

30:03.400 --> 30:04.920
You can see red!

30:05.160 --> 30:07.070
You can recognize color now!

30:09.270 --> 30:10.110
Lu!

30:11.400 --> 30:12.350
It's red!

30:38.960 --> 30:39.830
I thought

30:40.590 --> 30:42.520
you'd never see color in your life.

30:44.070 --> 30:45.160
What if this method

30:45.310 --> 30:46.440
doesn't work?

30:47.640 --> 30:48.200
Lu.

30:48.960 --> 30:50.680
We may be the same age,

30:51.350 --> 30:53.350
and equally strong in cultivation—

30:54.440 --> 30:55.370
but to be honest,

30:55.880 --> 30:56.830
all these years,

30:57.960 --> 31:00.160
I've always treated you like my own son.

31:06.790 --> 31:07.310
Right.

31:46.390 --> 31:47.740
[The Order of King Ding]

32:40.930 --> 32:44.650
[Emperor Zongding]

33:18.030 --> 33:19.110
Sir, you are here.

33:28.030 --> 33:29.310
After all these years,

33:30.480 --> 33:32.400
you still look exactly the same.

33:33.270 --> 33:34.800
You haven't changed at all.

33:35.550 --> 33:37.750
And this palace hasn't changed either.

33:37.880 --> 33:40.160
Not even a single tile has cracked.

33:40.830 --> 33:43.200
They say time spares no one—

33:44.400 --> 33:46.920
yet it seems I'm the only one

33:48.270 --> 33:50.240
being carried away by it.

33:50.790 --> 33:51.830
Time flies,

33:52.590 --> 33:53.590
and the body ages.

33:54.110 --> 33:55.640
It's inevitable, isn't it?

33:56.510 --> 33:57.880
You are right, Sir.

33:59.000 --> 33:59.440
Come.

33:59.790 --> 34:00.750
Please sit.

34:02.830 --> 34:04.890
Knowing you were coming to the capital,

34:04.890 --> 34:06.160
I specially had someone

34:06.160 --> 34:08.290
fetch cold wine from Wuquan Mountain.

34:09.070 --> 34:10.280
It was placed in the ice cellar

34:10.280 --> 34:12.000
for four hours.

34:13.320 --> 34:14.440
Sir, back then,

34:14.920 --> 34:16.880
this wine was your favorite.

34:17.630 --> 34:18.590
Try it.

34:19.230 --> 34:21.110
See if it tastes the same.

35:00.400 --> 35:02.740
All these years traveling the world,

35:03.900 --> 35:05.410
have you heard

35:05.430 --> 35:07.120
any rumors about me?

35:07.920 --> 35:08.710
Rumors?

35:09.400 --> 35:10.530
What kind of rumors?

35:10.760 --> 35:11.960
About my talent.

35:13.230 --> 35:14.920
You haven't heard, Sir?

35:15.400 --> 35:18.280
They say I excel
in calligraphy and painting.

35:18.400 --> 35:19.840
Inscriptions, calligraphy,

35:19.840 --> 35:21.590
and poetry, I excel in all.

35:22.590 --> 35:24.870
My brushstrokes are powerful and ethereal,

35:24.870 --> 35:26.530
as if guided by the immortals.

35:27.000 --> 35:27.920
I even have a title

35:27.920 --> 35:29.360
in the literary world—

35:29.800 --> 35:31.800
the Immortal of the Four Masteries.

35:32.110 --> 35:33.320
It means

35:33.880 --> 35:35.440
my calligraphy and painting

35:35.440 --> 35:36.970
can stir the winds and rain,

35:37.280 --> 35:39.210
and suppress both ghosts and gods.

35:40.360 --> 35:41.880
Have you heard of it, Sir?

35:47.480 --> 35:48.400
Sir,

35:48.940 --> 35:50.140
why are you laughing?

35:50.280 --> 35:51.810
I don't mean anything else.

35:52.400 --> 35:53.840
It's just that over these years,

35:53.840 --> 35:55.550
I've barely picked up a brush.

35:56.070 --> 35:57.320
So I wouldn't know much

35:57.320 --> 35:58.450
about these things.

35:58.550 --> 35:59.150
Really?

36:03.710 --> 36:05.070
I see.

36:05.920 --> 36:07.070
After we parted,

36:07.880 --> 36:10.280
I assumed you must've changed your name.

36:12.440 --> 36:14.370
But your talent was unparalleled—

36:15.710 --> 36:18.710
your calligraphy and paintings
were the best in the world.

36:18.710 --> 36:20.110
If you released a new work,

36:20.110 --> 36:21.910
it would surely shake the world.

36:22.320 --> 36:24.150
So I threw myself into it as well.

36:25.590 --> 36:28.720
I had people collect works
of calligraphy and painting.

36:29.800 --> 36:31.800
But there has been no word of you.

36:32.710 --> 36:34.440
People come and go in this life.

36:34.480 --> 36:35.440
It's like

36:35.710 --> 36:37.190
lonely geese drifting by the clouds,

36:37.190 --> 36:39.190
or duckweed floating upon the water.

36:39.190 --> 36:40.920
You shouldn't be too attached.

36:40.920 --> 36:41.590
Right.

36:43.400 --> 36:44.550
I thought so too.

36:46.000 --> 36:48.660
But you, Sir, have always
been a man of your word—

36:48.800 --> 36:50.730
your promises are as solid as gold.

36:53.110 --> 36:54.280
But Sir...

36:56.000 --> 36:56.960
This time,

36:59.670 --> 37:01.320
why did you come back?

37:15.400 --> 37:16.960
Why do you remain silent?

37:17.190 --> 37:18.520
What do you want to hear?

37:18.920 --> 37:20.070
Anything is fine.

37:21.120 --> 37:23.150
We, teacher and disciple,
haven't met for so many years.

37:23.150 --> 37:25.710
Shouldn't we reminisce about the past,

37:25.800 --> 37:28.000
or speak of the longing since our parting?

37:28.000 --> 37:29.860
Shouldn't we talk of old friends,

37:30.000 --> 37:31.460
or the world as it is today?

37:32.880 --> 37:33.680
Could it be...

37:34.670 --> 37:35.840
that you

37:37.200 --> 37:38.190
simply have nothing left

37:38.190 --> 37:39.360
to say to me?

37:48.110 --> 37:48.970
Are you afraid?

37:49.360 --> 37:50.110
Afraid?

37:51.440 --> 37:52.840
What would I have to fear?

37:53.110 --> 37:53.760
Indeed.

37:54.880 --> 37:56.540
What could you possibly fear?

37:57.550 --> 37:58.670
Now you have

37:58.670 --> 38:00.270
everything you ever wanted—

38:00.320 --> 38:01.480
a beautiful empire,

38:01.510 --> 38:02.970
and millions of citizens.

38:03.110 --> 38:04.510
Seated upon that throne,

38:05.440 --> 38:07.100
what could you possibly fear?

38:09.550 --> 38:11.190
I helped you to the throne back then,

38:11.190 --> 38:12.800
but it was a mere coincidence.

38:12.800 --> 38:14.070
I happened to enter the palace,

38:14.070 --> 38:16.150
and we happened to be master and student.

38:16.150 --> 38:17.760
It just so happened that at the time,

38:17.760 --> 38:19.960
you were someone agreeable to the eyes.

38:20.110 --> 38:21.670
It just so happened that at the time,

38:21.670 --> 38:23.320
the palace, from top to bottom,

38:23.320 --> 38:24.450
was a complete mess.

38:24.670 --> 38:26.400
Then I helped you along the way.

38:27.150 --> 38:28.680
I ask for nothing in return.

38:29.320 --> 38:30.920
I told you this a long time ago.

38:30.920 --> 38:32.230
Once you secured the throne,

38:32.230 --> 38:33.430
you wanted to kill me.

38:34.240 --> 38:34.790
But you know

38:34.790 --> 38:35.950
I am not a mortal,

38:36.550 --> 38:38.410
and you could never truly kill me.

38:40.150 --> 38:42.110
I had no intention of taking revenge.

38:42.110 --> 38:43.310
I always keep my word.

38:43.840 --> 38:45.640
So no matter how many years pass,

38:46.000 --> 38:47.800
you have nothing to fear from me.

38:50.440 --> 38:51.320
This time,

38:51.760 --> 38:53.290
I came for private matters.

38:55.230 --> 38:57.840
Does it involve
those cultivators from the immortal sects?

38:57.840 --> 38:59.190
It has nothing to do with you.

38:59.190 --> 39:00.920
You don't need to worry about it.

39:00.920 --> 39:02.050
In five days at most,

39:02.280 --> 39:03.680
I will leave the capital.

39:17.230 --> 39:17.840
Sir.

39:19.000 --> 39:19.590
Sir.

39:26.110 --> 39:26.960
Sir.

39:27.670 --> 39:29.400
Have you been to Beixiang?

39:30.800 --> 39:31.760
Back then,

39:32.430 --> 39:33.760
you painted a picture—

39:34.590 --> 39:35.920
Lonely mountains, ten thousand feet high,

39:35.920 --> 39:37.440
cloaked in endless snow.

39:38.400 --> 39:40.440
You said the sun in Beixiang
was wonderful,

39:40.440 --> 39:41.760
bright and fierce.

39:42.320 --> 39:43.550
When it rises,

39:43.550 --> 39:45.350
it's like gold paving the earth.

39:47.070 --> 39:48.800
You said that one day,

39:49.590 --> 39:51.440
you would see it for yourself.

39:51.960 --> 39:53.690
You said you would go there too.

39:54.480 --> 39:55.110
Yes.

39:55.670 --> 39:56.870
Did you ever go there?

39:58.840 --> 40:01.100
I'm not afraid of you laughing at me, Sir.

40:01.920 --> 40:03.850
When I was a kid reading my lessons,

40:04.560 --> 40:06.810
I believed our empire was boundless,

40:06.840 --> 40:08.900
possessing all within the four seas.

40:10.070 --> 40:11.890
I thought if one day

40:11.920 --> 40:13.510
I ascended the throne

40:13.800 --> 40:14.960
I'd look out toward the frontier,

40:14.960 --> 40:17.360
and see the magnificent scenery by myself.

40:20.960 --> 40:21.760
But now

40:23.480 --> 40:25.590
that I truly sit upon this throne,

40:29.720 --> 40:31.200
all I see

40:31.230 --> 40:33.480
are these square courtyards,

40:35.220 --> 40:37.580
and the ministers coming and going.

40:39.030 --> 40:41.150
I've longed to go out to see the world.

40:41.590 --> 40:44.000
But I am afraid of losing this throne.

40:45.400 --> 40:46.590
This throne—

40:48.920 --> 40:50.110
you carried me

40:51.070 --> 40:52.590
on your back,

40:53.840 --> 40:55.640
trudging through wind and snow,

40:56.000 --> 40:57.550
through dark alleys,

40:58.110 --> 41:00.880
through countless schemes,

41:01.150 --> 41:04.030
blood, and filth to seize it for me.

41:05.360 --> 41:06.360
If I lose it,

41:07.760 --> 41:09.800
there will never be anyone else

41:12.440 --> 41:13.630
to carry me

41:14.840 --> 41:16.510
and win it back again.

41:17.920 --> 41:18.480
Ding.

41:20.030 --> 41:21.160
You've already won.

41:23.070 --> 41:23.840
Relax.

41:24.930 --> 41:25.940
Get a good night's sleep.
